  <brief_title>Hypertrophic Scarring After Facial Burn</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hypertrophic Scarring After Facial Burn: A Pilot, Observational Study of Static and Dynamic Measurements of Facial Scars With the 3-D Scanner Through the Scar Maturation Process</official_title>
